ed="T" n="0803c07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0803c07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000011567"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>靈隱山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011071">道標</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0803c08"/><persName key="A011071">釋道標</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000012060">富陽</placeName>人也。俗姓<name>秦</name>氏，其遠祖與<persName key="A002762">羸</persName>同<lb
ed="T" n="0803c09"/>姓，世為<placeName key="PLG00000000091">汧隴</placeName>大族。及<placeName key="PL000000000103">晉</placeName>東渡衣冠隨之，後<lb
ed="T" n="0803c10"/>為<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>人也。其高、曾至王父<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1306"/>，皆沿以儒素，不<lb
ed="T" n="0803c11"/>甘為吏，故州里尊奉之。<persName key="A011071">標</persName>生則孤明，長而<lb
ed="T" n="0803c12"/>深趣，老而堅固，蓋良善之因有自來矣。<date key="j19935311993895" from-iso="+0746-01-01" to-iso="+0746-12-31">年<lb
ed="T" n="0803c13"/>七歲</date>時，神清氣茂，不雜凡童。倏有大沙門<lb
ed="T" n="0803c14"/>手摩其頂曰：「此<ref type="person" target="#A011071">孺子</ref>目秀如青蓮，得非我<lb
ed="T" n="0803c15"/><name>釋</name>氏之威鳳乎？苟能捨家，必有善稱。不然<lb
ed="T" n="0803c16"/>乘雲霓，薄天漢，吾不可得而知也。」父允<lb
ed="T" n="0803c17"/>其請，遂為<placeName key="PL000000011579"><placeName>靈隱山</placeName><placeName>白雲峯</placeName></placeName><persName key="A011131">海<roleName>和尚</roleName></persName>弟子。<placeName key="PL000000055454">妙<lb
ed="T" n="0803c18"/>高</placeName>之上，唯日月是麗；<persName key="A008480">娑竭</persName>之宮，固雲雷斯蓄。<lb
ed="T" n="0803c19"/><date from-iso="+0757-01-29" key="j19975771997960" to-iso="+0758-02-16"><name>至德</name>二年</date>，詔「白衣通佛經七百紙者，命為<lb
ed="T" n="0803c20"/>比丘」。<persName key="A011071">標</persName>首中其選，即日得度，蒙配<placeName key="PL000000011644">天竺寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1759"/><lb
ed="T" n="0803c21"/>焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0765-01-30" key="j20005002000672" notAfter-iso="+0765-07-21"><name>永泰</name>初</date>受具品於<placeName key="PL000000012759">靈光寺</placeName><persName key="A011134">顗<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>。登以護<lb
ed="T" n="0803c22"/>戒嚴謹，為時所推。毘奈多羅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>之言，罔不該<lb
ed="T" n="0803c23"/>貫。凡度人戒計六壇，為眾紏繩經一十二<lb
ed="T" n="0803c24"/>載。置田畝歲收萬斛，置無盡財<ptr type="glossary" target="#g645"/>，與眾共<lb
ed="T" n="0803c25"/>之。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242015139" notAfter-iso="+0805-02-28"><name>貞元</name>中</date>以寺務克豐，我宜宴息，乃擇高<lb
ed="T" n="0803c26"/>爽，得<placeName key="PL000000011567">西嶺</placeName>之下，葺茅為堂，不<anchor xml:id="beg0803sgsz15"/>干<anchor xml:id="end0803sgsz15"/>人事，用<lb
ed="T" n="0803c27"/>養浩氣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g2142"/>焉。<persName key="A011071">標</persName>經行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1047"/>之外，尤練詩章，辭體古<lb
ed="T" n="0803c28"/>健，比之<persName key="A010968">潘</persName>、<persName key="A019384">劉</persName>。當時<placeName key="PL000000013012">吳興</placeName>有<persName key="A008833">晝</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>有<persName key="A011069">靈澈</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0803c29"/>相與詶唱，遞作笙簧。故人諺云：「<placeName key="PL000000013012">霅</placeName>之<persName key="A008833">晝</persName>，能清<pb ed="T" n="0804a" xml:id="T50.2061.0804a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0804a01"/>秀；<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>之<persName key="A011069">澈</persName>，洞氷雪；<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>之<persName key="A011071">標</persName>，摩雲霄。」每飛章<lb
ed="T" n="0804a02"/>寓韻，竹夕<anchor xml:id="beg0804sgsz1"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0804sgsz1"/>時，彼三上人當四面之敵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g933"/>。所<lb
ed="T" n="0804a03"/>以辭林樂府常<anchor xml:id="beg0804sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>釆</sic><corr>采</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0804sgsz2"/>其聲詩。由是右庶子<placeName key="PL000000045043">姑臧</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0804a04"/><persName key="A023349">李<roleName>公</roleName>益</persName>書云：「重名之下果有斯文。西還<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京<lb
ed="T" n="0804a05"/>師</ref>，有以誇耀。」又<persName key="A010975"><persName>景陵子</persName><persName>陸羽</persName></persName>云：「夫日月雲<lb
ed="T" n="0804a06"/>霞為天標，山川草木為地標，推能歸美為<lb
ed="T" n="0804a07"/>德標，居閑趣寂為<persName key="A011071">道標</persName>。」名實兩全，品藻斯<lb
ed="T" n="0804a08"/>當。爾後聲價軼於公卿間，故與之深者有<lb
ed="T" n="0804a09"/>相國<persName key="A004369">李<roleName>公</roleName>吉甫</persName>、大司空<persName key="A004372">嚴<roleName>公</roleName>綬</persName>、右僕射<persName key="A011138"><anchor xml:id="beg0804sgsz3"/>韓<anchor xml:id="end0804sgsz3"/><roleName>公</roleName><lb
ed="T" n="0804a10"/>臯</persName>、禮部侍郎<persName key="A011140">呂<roleName>公</roleName>渭</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000024155">滑<anchor xml:id="beg0804sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>毫</sic><corr>亳</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0804sgsz7"/></placeName>節制<persName key="A011141">盧<roleName>公</roleName>群</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄陽</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0804a11"/>節制<persName key="A009184">孟<roleName>公</roleName>簡</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000043355">同州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A011142">李<roleName>公</roleName>敷</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔</placeName>尹<persName key="A011144">孫<roleName>公</roleName><lb
ed="T" n="0804a12"/>璹</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000011308">浙東</placeName>廉使<persName key="A011145">賈<roleName>公</roleName>全</persName>、中書舍人<persName key="A004029">白<roleName>公</roleName>居易</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000028309">隋<lb
ed="T" n="0804a13"/>州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A010166">劉<roleName>公</roleName>長卿</persName>、戶部侍<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>朗</sic><corr>郎</corr></choice><persName key="A010326">丘<roleName>公</roleName>丹</persName>、外郎<ptr type="glossary" target="#g381"/><persName key="A011146">裴<lb
ed="T" n="0804a14"/>樞</persName>、祕閣<ptr target="#n1760"/><persName key="A011070">嚴維</persName>、小諫<ptr type="glossary" target="#g648"/><persName key="A010966">朱放</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013239">越</placeName>廉問<ptr type="glossary" target="#g979"/><persName key="A011126">薛戎</persName>、夕拜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g646"/><persName key="A011147">盧<lb
ed="T" n="0804a15"/>元輔</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000009739">常州</placeName><persName key="A009613">釋元浩</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000010986">潤州</placeName><persName key="A011148">釋南容</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000013517">金華</placeName><persName key="A011149">釋乾輔</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0804a16"/><placeName key="PL000000009928">吳門</placeName><persName key="A011150">釋光嚴</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042189">上都</placeName><persName key="A011151">釋智崇</persName>等，並心交塵外，<lb
ed="T" n="0804a17"/>分契<ptr type="glossary" target="#g647"/>林中。萬境在空，驅之為射御；<placeName key="PL000000005250">五峯</placeName>滿<lb
ed="T" n="0804a18"/>眼，立之為疆<anchor xml:id="beg0804001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>場</sic><corr>埸</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0804001"/>。文雄而再鼓不衰，神王<lb
ed="T" n="0804a19"/>而一戰自勝者也。以<date from-iso="+0823-02-19" key="j20217042022057" to-iso="+0824-02-07"><name>長慶</name>三年</date>示有微疾，<lb
ed="T" n="0804a20"/><date key="j20218572021857" when-iso="+0823-07-22">六月七日</date>歸滅于所居蘭若。至冬<date key="j20219712021971" when-iso="+0823-11-13">十月<anchor xml:id="beg0804002"/>三<anchor xml:id="end0804002"/><lb
ed="T" n="0804a21"/>日</date>，葬于舊山，春秋八十有四，法臘五十八。<lb
ed="T" n="0804a22"/>弟子<persName key="A011154">如玢</persName>、<persName key="A011156">如𧦬</persName>、<persName key="A011157">行儉</persName>、<persName key="A011158">省言</persName>、<persName key="A011159">常儉</persName>、<persName key="A011160">智猷</persName>、<persName key="A011161">日超</persName>等，<lb
ed="T" n="0804a23"/>皆得師之法，倣仰不遑。空圍遶於栴檀，恨<lb
ed="T" n="0804a24"/>滿盈於石室，至今<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>民謂之<persName key="A011071">西嶺和尚</persName>矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0804a25"/><date notBefore-iso="+0840-02-11" key="j20279052028259" notAfter-iso="+0841-01-30"><name>開成</name>五年</date>中<persName key="A011153">鄭素卿</persName>錄德行刊碑頌，立于<lb
ed="T" n="0804a26"/><placeName key="PL000000011578">天竺山</placeName>之東墟存焉。</p>
